title: Mango Coconut Ice Cream
ingredients: ['200 ml coconut milk', '100 g mango puree', '50 g sugar']
directions: ['Blend coconut milk, mango puree, and sugar.', 'Churn in an ice cream maker and freeze until firm.', 'Serve cold.']

title: Rosemary Lemon Chicken
ingredients: ['4 chicken breasts', '10 g fresh rosemary', '20 ml lemon juice', '30 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Marinate chicken in rosemary, lemon juice, and olive oil for 30 minutes.', 'Bake at 180°C for 25 minutes.', 'Serve hot.']

title: Spicy Black Bean Tacos
ingredients: ['8 taco shells', '200 g black beans', '50 g salsa', '50 g shredded lettuce']
directions: ['Heat black beans and fill taco shells.', 'Top with salsa and shredded lettuce.', 'Serve immediately.']

title: Carrot Cake Energy Balls
ingredients: ['100 g oats', '50 g grated carrots', '20 g honey', '10 g raisins']
directions: ['Mix oats, grated carrots, honey, and raisins.', 'Roll into balls and chill before serving.', 'Store in the fridge.']

title: Green Smoothie
ingredients: ['1 banana', '100 g spinach', '200 ml almond milk', '10 g chia seeds']
directions: ['Blend banana, spinach, almond milk, and chia seeds until smooth.', 'Serve immediately.']

title: Stuffed Zucchini Boats
ingredients: ['2 zucchinis', '200 g ground turkey', '50 g tomato sauce', '50 g shredded cheese']
directions: ['Cut zucchinis in half and scoop out the center.', 'Fill with ground turkey and tomato sauce, and top with shredded cheese.', 'Bake at 180°C for 25 minutes.']

title: Peanut Butter Chocolate Smoothie
ingredients: ['1 banana', '30 g peanut butter', '200 ml milk', '10 g cocoa powder']
directions: ['Blend banana, peanut butter, milk, and cocoa powder until smooth.', 'Serve chilled.']

title: Lemon Dill Salmon
ingredients: ['4 salmon fillets', '10 g dill', '20 ml lemon juice', '30 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Marinate salmon in dill, lemon juice, and olive oil for 15 minutes.', 'Bake at 180°C for 20 minutes.', 'Serve with a side of vegetables.']

title: Chocolate Avocado Pudding
ingredients: ['2 ripe avocados', '50 g cocoa powder', '50 g honey', '100 ml almond milk']
directions: ['Blend avocados, cocoa powder, honey, and almond milk until smooth.', 'Chill before serving.', 'Garnish with berries if desired.']

title: Lentil Veggie Burgers
ingredients: ['200 g lentils', '50 g breadcrumbs', '50 g grated carrots', '10 g garlic']
directions: ['Mash cooked lentils and mix with breadcrumbs, grated carrots, and minced garlic.', 'Form into patties and pan-fry until golden.', 'Serve on a bun with toppings.']

title: Pineapple Salsa
ingredients: ['200 g pineapple', '50 g red onion', '10 g cilantro', '10 ml lime juice']
directions: ['Dice pineapple and red onion.', 'Mix with chopped cilantro and lime juice.', 'Serve as a topping or dip.']

title: Herb Roasted Sweet Potatoes
ingredients: ['500 g sweet potatoes', '10 g rosemary', '30 ml olive oil', '5 g salt']
directions: ['Cut sweet potatoes into cubes.', 'Toss with rosemary, olive oil, and salt.', 'Roast at 200°C for 25 minutes.']

title: Zucchini Noodles with Pesto
ingredients: ['2 zucchinis', '50 g pesto', '10 g Parmesan cheese', '10 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Spiralize zucchinis into noodles.', 'Toss with pesto and olive oil.', 'Top with grated Parmesan and serve.']

title: Chickpea Curry
ingredients: ['200 g chickpeas', '50 g curry paste', '400 ml coconut milk', '200 ml vegetable stock']
directions: ['Simmer chickpeas in vegetable stock.', 'Stir in curry paste and coconut milk.', 'Cook for 10 minutes and serve with rice.']

title: Berry Yogurt Parfait
ingredients: ['200 g Greek yogurt', '100 g mixed berries', '50 g granola', '10 g honey']
directions: ['Layer Greek yogurt, mixed berries, granola, and honey in a glass.', 'Repeat layers and serve chilled.']

title: Baked Eggplant Parmesan
ingredients: ['2 eggplants', '200 g tomato sauce', '100 g mozzarella', '50 g breadcrumbs']
directions: ['Slice eggplants and layer with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and breadcrumbs in a baking dish.', 'Bake at 180°C for 30 minutes until bubbly and golden.', 'Serve warm.']

title: Spaghetti Squash Alfredo
ingredients: ['1 spaghetti squash', '200 ml cream', '50 g Parmesan cheese', '10 g garlic']
directions: ['Roast spaghetti squash at 200°C for 40 minutes.', 'Scoop out strands and toss with cream, Parmesan, and garlic.', 'Serve hot.']

title: Cauliflower Buffalo Wings
ingredients: ['1 head cauliflower', '50 g flour', '50 ml hot sauce', '30 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Cut cauliflower into florets.', 'Toss with flour and olive oil, then bake at 200°C for 20 minutes.', 'Coat with hot sauce and bake for another 10 minutes.']

title: Lemon Herb Risotto
ingredients: ['200 g arborio rice', '1 liter vegetable stock', '10 ml lemon juice', '10 g parsley']
directions: ['Cook arborio rice in vegetable stock, stirring constantly.', 'Add lemon juice and parsley before serving.', 'Serve warm.']

title: Roasted Garlic Hummus
ingredients: ['200 g canned chickpeas', '50 g tahini', '10 ml lemon juice', '1 head roasted garlic']
directions: ['Blend chickpeas, tahini, lemon juice, and roasted garlic until smooth.', 'Serve with pita bread or vegetables.']

title: Caprese Salad
ingredients: ['200 g cherry tomatoes', '100 g mozzarella', '10 g basil', '20 ml balsamic glaze']
directions: ['Slice cherry tomatoes and mozzarella.', 'Arrange on a plate and top with basil and balsamic glaze.', 'Serve immediately.']

title: Spinach Feta Stuffed Chicken
ingredients: ['4 chicken breasts', '100 g spinach', '50 g feta cheese', '10 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Cut a pocket into each chicken breast.', 'Stuff with spinach and feta mixture and secure with toothpicks.', 'Bake at 180°C for 25 minutes.']

title: Tomato Lentil Soup
ingredients: ['200 g red lentils', '1 liter vegetable stock', '200 g diced tomatoes', '10 g cumin']
directions: ['Combine lentils, vegetable stock, diced tomatoes, and cumin in a pot.', 'Simmer for 25 minutes and blend partially for a creamy texture.', 'Serve warm.']

title: Zucchini Fritters
ingredients: ['500 g zucchini', '50 g flour', '1 egg', '5 g salt']
directions: ['Grate zucchini and squeeze out excess water.', 'Mix with flour, egg, and salt.', 'Fry spoonfuls in hot oil until golden.', 'Serve warm.']

title: Miso Soup
ingredients: ['1 liter water', '50 g miso paste', '100 g tofu', '10 g seaweed']
directions: ['Heat water and dissolve miso paste.', 'Add tofu and seaweed and simmer for 5 minutes.', 'Serve hot.']

title: Berry Oat Bars
ingredients: ['200 g oats', '100 g mixed berries', '50 g honey', '50 g butter']
directions: ['Mix oats, honey, and melted butter.', 'Press half the mixture into a baking dish and top with berries.', 'Cover with remaining oat mixture and bake at 180°C for 25 minutes.', 'Cool and slice into bars.']

title: Roasted Red Pepper Dip
ingredients: ['200 g roasted red peppers', '50 g cream cheese', '10 ml lemon juice', '10 g garlic']
directions: ['Blend roasted red peppers, cream cheese, lemon juice, and garlic until smooth.', 'Serve with crackers or bread.']

title: Chickpea Avocado Salad
ingredients: ['200 g canned chickpeas', '1 avocado', '10 ml lemon juice', '10 g cilantro']
directions: ['Mash avocado and mix with chickpeas, lemon juice, and chopped cilantro.', 'Serve as a side dish or sandwich filling.']

title: Cauliflower Mash
ingredients: ['500 g cauliflower', '50 ml cream', '10 g garlic', '5 g salt']
directions: ['Boil cauliflower until tender.', 'Blend with cream, garlic, and salt until smooth.', 'Serve as a low-carb side dish.']

title: Chocolate Chia Pudding
ingredients: ['200 ml almond milk', '50 g chia seeds', '20 gn  cocoa powder', '20 g honey']
directions: ['Mix almond milk, chia seeds, cocoa powder, and honey.', 'Chill for 4 hours, stirring occasionally.', 'Serve chilled.']

title: Sweet Potato Black Bean Tacos
ingredients: ['4 taco shells', '200 g black beans', '100 g sweet potato', '50 g salsa']
directions: ['Roast sweet potato cubes at 200°C for 25 minutes.', 'Fill taco shells with black beans, roasted sweet potatoes, and salsa.', 'Serve immediately.']

title: Lemon Herb Couscous
ingredients: ['200 g couscous', '10 g parsley', '10 ml lemon juice', '20 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Cook couscous according to package instructions.', 'Toss with parsley, lemon juice, and olive oil.', 'Serve warm or chilled.']

title: Vegetable Stir-Fry
ingredients: ['200 g mixed vegetables', '50 ml soy sauce', '10 ml sesame oil', '10 g ginger']
directions: ['Heat sesame oil in a pan and sauté ginger.', 'Add mixed vegetables and stir-fry for 5 minutes.', 'Stir in soy sauce and cook for another 2 minutes.', 'Serve over rice or noodles.']

title: Avocado Toast with Egg
ingredients: ['2 slices bread', '1 avocado', '2 eggs', '10 ml lemon juice']
directions: ['Toast bread slices.', 'Mash avocado with lemon juice and spread on toast.', 'Top with fried eggs and serve.']

title: Banana Oat Pancakes
ingredients: ['2 bananas', '100 g oats', '2 eggs', '10 g cinnamon']
directions: ['Blend bananas, oats, eggs, and cinnamon into a smooth batter.', 'Cook pancakes on a non-stick skillet until golden.', 'Serve warm with maple syrup.']

title: Grilled Vegetable Skewers
ingredients: ['200 g zucchini', '200 g bell peppers', '100 g mushrooms', '30 ml olive oil']
directions: ['Cut vegetables into chunks and toss with olive oil.', 'Thread onto skewers and grill for 10 minutes, turning occasionally.', 'Serve warm.']

title: Strawberry Spinach Salad
ingredients: ['100 g spinach', '200 g strawberries', '30 g almonds', '20 ml balsamic dressing']
directions: ['Toss spinach, sliced strawberries, and almonds together.', 'Drizzle with balsamic dressing and serve immediately.']

title: Quinoa Breakfast Bowl
ingredients: ['200 g quinoa', '1 banana', '30 g almonds', '10 g honey']
directions: ['Cook quinoa and let cool slightly.', 'Top with sliced banana, almonds, and a drizzle of honey.', 'Serve as a healthy breakfast.']

title: Lentil Spinach Curry
ingredients: ['200 g lentils', '100 g spinach', '400 ml coconut milk', '50 g curry paste']
directions: ['Cook lentils in water until tender.', 'Stir in curry paste, coconut milk, and spinach.', 'Simmer for 10 minutes and serve with rice.']

title: Mediterranean Pasta Salad
ingredients: ['200 g pasta', '50 g cherry tomatoes', '50 g olives', '30 g feta cheese']
directions: ['Cook pasta and cool.', 'Mix with cherry tomatoes, olives, and crumbled feta cheese.', 'Toss with olive oil and serve chilled.']

title: Pineapple Sandwich
ingredients: ['2 slices of white bread', '4 pineapple rings (canned or fresh)', '2 tbsp mayonnaise', 'Salt to taste']
directions: ['Spread 1 tbsp of mayonnaise evenly on each slice of bread.', 'Place a pineapple ring on two slices of bread.', 'Sprinkle with a pinch of salt if desired.', 'Top with the remaining slices of bread to form sandwiches.']

title: Pineapple Fluff
ingredients: ['1 can (20 oz) crushed pineapple, drained', '1 package (3.4 oz) instant vanilla pudding mix', '2 cups whipped topping', '1 cup mini marshmallows', '1/2 cup chopped pecans']
directions: ['In a large bowl, combine the drained crushed pineapple and instant vanilla pudding mix.', 'Fold in the whipped topping until well blended.', 'Stir in the mini marshmallows and chopped pecans.', 'Refrigerate for at least 1 hour before serving.']

title: Waffled Pizza Dippers
ingredients: ['1 tube (13.8 oz) refrigerated pizza dough', '1/2 cup pizza sauce', '1 cup shredded mozzarella cheese', '1/2 cup sliced pepperoni (optional)', '1/4 cup melted butter', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp Italian seasoning']
directions: ['Preheat a waffle iron and lightly grease it.', 'Roll out the pizza dough and cut it into 4 equal rectangles.', 'Spread pizza sauce on half of each rectangle, leaving a small border.', 'Sprinkle with mozzarella cheese and add pepperoni if using.', 'Fold the dough over and seal the edges by pressing with a fork.', 'Brush the tops with melted butter mixed with garlic powder and Italian seasoning.', 'Place one filled dough rectangle in the waffle iron and cook until golden brown.', 'Repeat with the remaining dough rectangles.', 'Cut into strips and serve with extra pizza sauce for dipping.']

title: Fried Twinkies
ingredients: ['6 Twinkies', '6 wooden skewers', '4 cups vegetable oil (for frying)', '1 cup milk', '2 Tbsp vinegar', '1 Tbsp vegetable oil', '1 cup all-purpose flour', '1 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp salt', 'Powdered sugar (for dusting)']
directions: ['Insert wooden skewers into the Twinkies and freeze them for at least 2 hours.', 'Heat vegetable oil in a deep fryer or large pot to 375°F (190°C).', 'In a bowl, mix milk, vinegar, and 1 Tbsp vegetable oil; let sit for 5 minutes.', 'Combine flour, baking powder, and salt in another bowl.', 'Gradually whisk the dry ingredients into the wet ingredients until smooth.', 'Dip each frozen Twinkie into the batter, coating it completely.', 'Carefully lower the Twinkies into the hot oil and fry until golden brown, about 2-3 minutes.', 'Remove and drain on paper towels.', 'Dust with powdered sugar before serving.']

title: Fried Milk
ingredients: ['2 cups milk', '1/2 cup cornstarch', '1/4 cup sugar', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '1 cup all-purpose flour', '2 eggs, beaten', '1 cup breadcrumbs', 'Vegetable oil (for frying)', 'Powdered sugar (for dusting, optional)']
directions: ['In a saucepan, combine milk, cornstarch, sugar, and vanilla extract over medium heat.', 'Cook while stirring constantly until the mixture thickens and becomes smooth.', 'Pour the mixture into a greased square dish and refrigerate for at least 2 hours, or until firm.', 'Cut the chilled milk mixture into small squares or rectangles.', 'Prepare three bowls for coating: one with flour, one with beaten eggs, and one with breadcrumbs.', 'Coat each piece of milk first in flour, then in egg, and finally in breadcrumbs.', 'Heat vegetable oil in a deep fryer or large skillet to 350°F (175°C).', 'Fry the coated milk pieces until golden brown, about 2-3 minutes.', 'Drain on paper towels and dust with powdered sugar if desired before serving.']
